---
title: Carrot and Tomato Soup with basil, mozzarella and baguette
description: The only thing better than a warm bowl of soup for dinner is a crusty melty mozzarella baguette to have along with it. The carrots and basil make this dish vibrant both in colour and in taste.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221007_R10_W48_IE_IEXFVCLV0073-1_KB_Main_5_high-1e1a2a93.jpg
